Description: Based on data officially reported by the National Statistics and Censuses Institute of Argentina. The International Monetary Fund (IMF) has called on Argentina to adopt measures to address the quality of official GDP and consumer price index data, and issued an updated statement on Argentina’s progress on June 3, 2015: http://www.imf.org/external/np/sec/pr/2015/pr15252.htm.
Covers mainland Tanzania only.
